					"value": "Go to Guildhall. (S_LOW_Guildhall_Entrance_a78a0b7b-489a-4743-9e6e-4c88f24cc2ca)\r\n\r\nSwap Roah with Friol by using ReCon: \r\noe Guildhall_Swap_ZhentLeader \r\n\r\nRecruit Minsc + optionally jaheira\r\n\r\nInitiate the Zhent takeover of the Guild by using ReCon: \r\noe Guildhall_ZhentBetrayal"
