				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Origin moment for Minsc + Jaheira with Boss Friol.\r\nAfter Minsc learns of the Zhentarim plans to overthrow Nine-Fingers, he returns to the Guildhall to confront their leader, Roah. She taunts him with his past evil deeds as the 'Stone Lord' - the player decideds whether to back Minsc and fight Roah, or let Roah's plan come to fruition for the 'greater good'."
				}
			}
